{
  "page": "Did you know/97",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>... that the name and sigil of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Willum\" title=\"House Willum\">House Willum</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> as well as the names of Lord Willum's two sons, <a href=\"/index.php/Josua_Willum\" title=\"Josua Willum\">Josua</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Elyas_Willum\" title=\"Elyas Willum\">Elyas</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rssm996.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rssm996.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> are a tribute to the <i><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Memory,_Sorrow,_and_Thorn\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Memory, Sorrow, and Thorn\">Memory, Sorrow, and Thorn</a></i> series of his colleague <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tad_Williams\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Tad Williams\">Tad Williams</a>?\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Did_you_know/97&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The Citadel: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.westeros.org/Citadel/Heraldry/Houses/7/\">Heraldry - In the Reach</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rssm996.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rssm996.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/So_Spake_Martin\" title=\"So Spake Martin\">So Spake M